//   notes:         Trivial file. Cross-crate refs (state.require_lib,
//                  state.pop_n, crate::*::open) resolve in Phase B.
//                  Phase B must also reconcile inconsistent open-function
//                  names in the existing stdlib modules (see PORT NOTEs).
// ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

